HEADWORD: Arianize
<hw>A"ri*an*ize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To admit or
accept the tenets of the Arians; to become an Arian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Arianize</ent>⟦br⟧

